beer.beer_description: What could be easier than sitting down with your mates, in the pub, for a nice cool glass of Porter? This sessionable porter has notes of toasted biscuit and chocolate finishing with a classic bite from UK Goldings hops. Whether you’re drinking it straight from the can, or poured by your preferred Publican, Easy Peasy Porter lives up to its name and will have you chuffed to bits!

Hoppy International Beer Day!

Beer serves as the common thread that links us worldwide, possessing the ability to bring people together in a unique way.

Beer has played a significant role in shaping countless of our most cherished memories. And if there’s one thing we’ve learned along the way, beer is best when shared with others.
